  "texts": [
    "Through experiments and detailed analysis at each stage based on the model, this study clarified the importance of preventing intent degradation and loss during speech and keyword extraction.",
    "From the perspective of preventing intent degradation in speech, one of the study's key findings is the practical improvement point of structuring dialogue to ensure all elements of the 6W1H needs model are fully addressed.",
    "This research successfully modeled the often ambiguous process of capturing user intent for service development and concretized and implemented it based on our prior studies.",
    "The abstract model presents potential for further expansion and alternative applications, such as extracting intent not only from speech but also from context, and extending beyond upcycling case presentation to real-time development support, similar to GitHub Copilot.",
    "These possibilities open avenues for future research and development.Limitations of the proposed method are discussed."
